name: Little Red Riding Hood Dress
description:
This dress is made from high quality 100% Cotton.

The main fabric is Pink with a Red Riding Hood theme. It is perfectly complimented by a matching trim.

As your child grows this bow can be loosened to give more room under the arms and it looks equally gorgeous worn as a top with a pair of leggings.
